commit.message: Add support for CFFI pointers for Vulkan objects

Fix TypeError(s) when initialising GamePad state

The initialisers for buttons (and axes) require integer (or float)
arguments, but got arrays instead.

Fixed by unpacking the arrays.
Add wheel for manylinux2014 with wayland support
Use wheel tags for individual python versions
Improve Linux and macOS installation notes
ENH: Rework library loading on Win to add better conda support
Add wrappers for GLFW native functions
Include Visual C++ runtime DLLs in Windows wheels
